00:50:14,560 --> 00:50:16,560
 So there was a thing which I didn't know about,

1067
00:50:16,560 --> 00:50:21,680
 which went from 1915 all the way up to the 1950s called race films.

1068
00:50:21,680 --> 00:50:25,120
