1083
00:50:57,440 --> 00:50:59,440
 "Look, there's a load of old tapes here.

1084
00:50:59,440 --> 00:51:01,600
 They're just taking up a load of space.

1085
00:51:01,600 --> 00:51:02,880
 We're going to get rid of them.

1086
00:51:02,880 --> 00:51:04,480
 Do you want to have a look through them?"

1087
00:51:04,480 --> 00:51:06,480
 And he went, "Okay, well, I'm going to have a look through them."

1088
00:51:06,480 --> 00:51:08,960
 And it turned out that it was all of these old,

1089
00:51:08,960 --> 00:51:10,320
 what they call, race films.

1090
00:51:10,320 --> 00:51:11,920
 And now we have loads of them back

1091
00:51:11,920 --> 00:51:14,640
 and they're restoring them all and people can watch them again.

1092
00:51:14,640 --> 00:51:15,600
 - Wow. - Isn't that cool?

1093
00:51:15,600 --> 00:51:17,200
 That is so cool.

